Package: cornet
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Elastic Net with Dichotomised Outcomes
Description: Implements lasso and ridge regression for dichotomised outcomes (Rauschenberger et al. 2024, <doi:10.1080/02664763.2023.2233057>). Such outcomes are not naturally but artificially binary. They indicate whether an underlying measurement is greater than a threshold.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: glmnet, palasso
Suggests: knitr, testthat, rmarkdown
Enhances: RColorBrewer, MASS, mvtnorm, randomForest, xgboost, MLmetrics
Authors@R: person("Armin","Rauschenberger",email="armin.rauschenberger@uni.lu",role=c("aut","cre"))
VignetteBuilder: knitr
